---
title: Pesto Shrimp Naan with Mozzarella Cheese
description: Juicy pan-fried shrimp, rich pesto and tender peppers are the star of these pizza-style naan! A flourish of mozzarella and sprinkling of chili flakes add a creamy and spicy kick.
